<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11347</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧被绑在房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他听见自己的徒弟正对着妖怪叫喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把唐僧交出来！”八戒叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！唐僧听到了兵器撞击的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“希望他们可以把我救出去。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34496</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个年轻的女子走进了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你......你是谁？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我被关在这里。”女子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“13年前，那个妖怪把我抓到这里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不让我离开。你能帮帮我吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也希望我可以帮助你。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他给女子看了绑住他的绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮你解开绳子。”女子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71040</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你能帮我带一封信给我的父母吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然。”唐僧说，“你的父母是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们是宝象国的国王和王后。”女子说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是百花公主。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净依然在和妖怪打斗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 这时，公主跑到了外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王！”她大叫，“我需要你的帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99850</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪立刻停止了打斗，转向公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以为你做什么，亲爱的？”妖怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“里面有个和尚。”公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到他被绑起来，我很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你能放他走吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那和尚不是普通的和尚。他是……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，百花公主假装哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133395</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪举起了手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135664</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，好了，亲爱的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135665</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只要你高兴，我就放了那个和尚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪跟着公主回到了宝塔里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒和悟净困惑地看了看彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那妖怪要放了唐僧？”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，唐僧出来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157751</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有件事必须去做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地跟他的徒弟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天下午，他们到了宝象国的宫殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后正在读她女儿写来的信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛里充满泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可怜的女儿。”王后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这么多年，她一直被关着。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王站了起来，眼睛里冒着怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193598</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上命令身边的侍卫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193599</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196581</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“召集你的部队。”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196582</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一定要打败那妖怪，救出我的女儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，陛下。”侍卫长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们只是凡人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们怎么才能打败那个厉害的妖怪呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的两个徒弟都很厉害，陛下。”唐僧开口说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我保证，他们会把您的女儿救回来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，八戒和悟净回到了宝塔那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒举起他的钉耙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238212</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哗啦！宝塔门被砸开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“妖怪，出来！”他大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪跑了出来。“你太过分了！”他大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247314</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我都放那个和尚走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们为什么还砸坏我的门？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来这里接公主回去。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是宝象国的国王派我们来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260472</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264628</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们不可能带公主走的。”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264629</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们很相爱。”八戒和悟净发起了攻击。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪挡住了他们的兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277331</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打了一个多小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277332</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，八戒打累了，转身跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净非常生气。“八戒！”他大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你去哪里——啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪打倒了悟净，并把他捆了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把悟净拖进了宝塔，锁在一个房间里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王知道公主在这里。”妖怪自言自语地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是怎么知道的？”他摸着下巴思考着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“公主一定是让那个和尚给国王带信了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他眼睛里冒着怒火。“她骗了我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>